  m_text: "Privacy Policy\n\nLast Updated: [Date]\nApp Name: NEOBLOCK\n\nNEOBLOCK
    is a free-to-play mobile puzzle game supported by advertisements.\n\nWe do not
    collect personally identifiable information such as name, email address, or contact
    details unless you voluntarily contact us.\n\nAdvertising\n\nThe Game displays
    third-party advertisements to support development.\nAdvertising partners may
    collect limited device information such as:\n\nDevice type\n\nOperating system
    version\n\nAnonymous device identifiers\n\nAdvertising interaction data\n\nAds
    may be personalized or non-personalized depending on your device settings and
    region.\n\nUsers may manage advertising preferences in their device privacy settings.\n\nAnalytics\n\nWe
    may collect anonymous usage data including:\n\nLevel progress\n\nSession duration\n\nGameplay
    performance\n\nCrash reports\n\nThis information is used solely to improve the
    Game experience.\n\nData Sharing\n\nWe do not sell personal data.\nNon-personal
    data may be shared with advertising and analytics partners for service functionality.\n\nChildren\u2019s
    Privacy\n\nThe Game is intended for a general audience.\nWe do not knowingly
    collect personal data from children.\n\nContact\n\nFor privacy-related questions:\n[emrecangarip1907@gmail.com]\nhttps://docs.google.com/document/d/1iU3qNmQZofiGD13OyeNRqxei7Wq-GVfhQm5qgnScb9c/edit?usp=sharing"
