    m_PersistentCalls:
      m_Calls: []
  m_text: "-Level Mode (99 Levels)\n\nProgress through 99 carefully designed levels
    with increasing difficulty.\nEach stage challenges you to think ahead, place
    blocks strategically, and clear objectives efficiently to achieve the highest
    possible score.\n\n-Start Mode (Classic Mode)\n\nEnjoy an endless classic experience.\nPlace
    your blocks wisely and survive as long as possible. The game ends when there
    is no remaining space on the grid, so every move matters.\n\n-Block Refresh System\n\nA
    Block Refresh button is located at the top-left corner of the screen.\n\nIt can
    be used once for free during each gameplay session.\n\nAdditional refreshes can
    be unlocked by watching a rewarded ad.\n\nUse it strategically \u2014 the right
    moment can completely change the outcome of your game.\n\n-Scoring System\n\nEvery
    fully completed horizontal or vertical line awards +100 points.\n\nClearing multiple
    lines at once significantly increases your total score.\n\nAs levels progress,
    smarter planning and forward thinking become essential.\n\n\"If you are ready
    to test your logic, improve your strategy, and aim for the highest score,\nNEOBLOCK
    is waiting for you.\""
  m_isRightToLeft: 0
  m_fontAsset: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 8f586378b4e144a9851e7b34d9b748ee, type: 2}
